DFA
***

This manual describes the installation and usage of `DFA' V1.2. Here
you'll find the explanation of all the AREXX commands as well. If you
use a localized Workbench (Workbench V2.1 and better) and have set it
to a language other than English, please notice that I'll refer to the
English program texts in this documentation!


