@Node "The Error Codes" "dfa_english.guide/The Error Codes"
@Next "ArexxTable"
@Prev "The Arexx Commands"
@Toc "The Arexx Port"

The Error Codes
===============

The error code are the same as given by the AREXX manual:
     0:   No error
     5:   Warning
     10:  Error
     20:  Severe error

If something goes wrong while working on a command, `DFA' returns `10'
(`RC_ERROR') in RC! If there is a syntax error, the AREXX command
parser returns `20'.


@EndNode

